{"title":"场上小语","authors":["李映青"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上小语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李映青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让天再高三丈三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦堆高大像金山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金山顶顶撞着了天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摊了半天场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只搬了个山尖尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“麦堆高了显天低"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要给老天打个无线电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年麦堆要比今年高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它再高三丈三”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑歌声里扬场忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一锨，我一杈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦颗落个哗哗哗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像天上把金颗下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会积了个金圪答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年都有金圪答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年那有今年大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因实现公社化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉心里开了花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神抖擞扬的欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴愉快说了话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小伙子们加油扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看老汉这几下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天去把公粮送"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再听大叔的鞭子叭、叭、叭”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满场笑声撒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装的装、拉的拉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会计的算盘吧啦啦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二一添作五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五四倍作八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“亩产上了五百八！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声、笑声，满场撒"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}